-Oh, God. You hear a buzzing?

260
00:17:39,004 --> 00:17:41,302
Come on, we got a show to do.

261
00:17:41,507 --> 00:17:44,704
-l can`t focus.
-But there`s nothing wrong.

262
00:17:44,910 --> 00:17:48,175
Then why does he want more tests?

263
00:17:48,381 --> 00:17:50,008
He has to rule out things.

264
00:17:50,216 --> 00:17:53,014
-Like what?
-l don`t know. Cancer.

265
00:17:53,219 --> 00:17:56,711
Don`t say that.
l don`t wanna hear that word.

266
00:17:56,922 --> 00:17:58,719
