00:20:33,579 --> 00:20:36,810
-That`s unpolished red granite.
-ls it?

315
00:20:37,016 --> 00:20:40,383
-lt has an organic quality.
-Right.

316
00:20:40,586 --> 00:20:44,078
Entirely interdependent,
if you know what l mean.

317
00:20:44,290 --> 00:20:48,920
l can`t put it into words.
The important thing is, it breathes.

318
00:20:49,128 --> 00:20:52,655
April, people pass by vital
structures all the time.

319
00:20:52,865 --> 00:20:54,924
They never appreciate them.

320
00:20:55,134 --> 00:20:57,466
You tune into your environment.

321
00:20:57,670 --> 00:21:01,071
-lt`s important.
